title: NFL Round 2 Day 2
author: VD
content_html: Minor upset and major upset yesterday. The Ravens knocking off the Titans wasn’t shocking, the Cardinals blowing away the Panthers was. I’m 0-2, but I still like New York and Pittsburgh. I mean, home teams have never gone 0-4, have they?
